INTRODUCTION
============

K8 is a Javascript shell built upon the Google v8 Javascript engine. Most
importantly, it extends v8 with a `File' object.

K8 also comes with a Javascript library independent of the K8 shell.


INSTALL
=======

1. Check out the Google v8 Javascript engine from http://code.google.com/p/v8/

2. Compile v8 to generate libv8.a

3. Copy k8.cc in this repository to the root of the v8 source code tree.

4. Compile k8 with: g++ -Isrc -O3 -Wall k8.cc -o k8 -lz -lpthread libv8.a

For example:

  svn co http://v8.googlecode.com/svn/tags/3.0.6.1 v8
  cd v8
  scons snapshot=on arch=x64
  cp PATH_TO/k8.cc .
  g++ -Isrc -O3 -Wall k8.cc -o k8 -lz -lpthread libv8.a
